item.title: Clickage2 Winned
item.dc:creator: @Starblaster100 Starblaster100
item.description:
@Starblaster100 wrote:

[quote=“Miss Silabsoft, post:1, topic:21175”][scar]program Clickage2Winned;
//Game: http://addictinggames.com/clickage2.html
//Setup Select window and run.
//Press go and watch carnage
//By MissSilabSoft
var
somenumber:Integer;
Round1,Round2,Round3:Boolean;

procedure Clickit;
begin
repeat;
ClickMouse(200, 50, True);
somenumber:= somenumber + 1;
until(somenumber = 100);
end;

begin
repeat
if(GetColor(46,271) = 255)then
begin
Clickit;
somenumber:= 0;
Round1:= True
end;
if(GetColor(369,524) = 255)then
begin
Clickit;
somenumber:= 0;
Round2:= True
end;
if(GetColor(527,299) = 255)then
begin
Clickit;
somenumber:= 0;
Round3:= True
end;

until(Round1 = True) and (Round2 = True) and (Round3 = True);
end.[/scar][/quote]
owned.
